Here's a PlantUML sequence diagram representing the control flow for the Nishu0_anime_nft_marketplace system:

```plantuml
@startuml Nishu0_anime_nft_marketplace

actor User
participant "React Frontend" as Frontend
participant "NFTContext" as Context
participant "Web3Modal" as Web3Modal
participant "Smart Contract" as Contract
participant "IPFS" as IPFS

User -> Frontend : Interacts with UI
Frontend -> Context : Requests action
Context -> Web3Modal : Connect wallet
Web3Modal --> Context : Return wallet connection

alt Create NFT
    Context -> IPFS : Upload metadata
    IPFS --> Context : Return metadata URI
    Context -> Contract : Mint NFT
    Contract --> Context : Confirm minting
else List NFT for sale
    Context -> Contract : List NFT
    Contract --> Context : Confirm listing
else Buy NFT
    Context -> Contract : Purchase NFT
    Contract -> Contract : Transfer ownership
    Contract --> Context : Confirm purchase
else Fetch NFTs
    Context -> Contract : Request NFT data
    Contract --> Context : Return NFT data
end

Context --> Frontend : Update state
Frontend --> User : Display result

@enduml
```